Aim
To create a new process using the fork() system call and display the Process ID (PID) of the current process and its parent process using getpid() and getppid() system calls.
PSUEDO CODE
Start
Call fork()
If child process then
    Display Current Process ID using getpid()
    Display Parent Process ID using getppid()
Else
    Display Current Process ID using getpid()
    Display Parent Process ID using getppid()
End If

Stop
